# Next.js Interview Application

This is a Next.js application with TypeScript, authentication via NextAuth, and Microsoft Clarity for analytics. Used for AI-based mock software engineering interviews.

## Repository Structure
- src/app - Next.js app router pages and API routes
- src/components - React components organized by feature
- src/lib - Auth, API services, and utilities
- src/utils - Helper functions
- src/constants - Application constants
- src/types - TypeScript type definitions
- src/hooks - Custom React hooks

## Coding Standards
- TypeScript with strict typing (avoid 'any')
- Functional React components with hooks
- Error handling with meaningful messages
- DRY principle and SRP (SOLID)
- Environment variables for configuration
- Layout-level authentication checks
- WCAG accessibility compliance
